<div class="entry-content cf">
	
	
					<div class="entry-thumbnail">
				<a class="post-thumbnail" href="http://www.2ndcouncilhouse.co.uk/blog/2012/02/03/the-destruction-of-the-metropole/">
									</a>
			</div>
		
		<div class="entry-excerpt"><a href="http://www.2ndcouncilhouse.co.uk/blog/2012/02/03/the-destruction-of-the-metropole/"></a><div class="otw-row">
<div class="otw-twentyfour otw-columns"><a href="http://www.2ndcouncilhouse.co.uk/blog/2012/02/03/the-destruction-of-the-metropole/"></a>
<p>It is an odd situation that Scotland finds herself in at the moment.&nbsp; A bit like a teenager, yearning for the freedom which is only a few years away but seems like a lifetime is to be lived until the magic date which will denote the beginning of our independence.&nbsp; And like a teenager we &#8230;</p>
</div>
<p>&hellip;</p></div>
